      "text": "Yesterday [[Mani Matter]] once again opened his notebook, \"in which I have not written anything down for such a long time. While reading the notes from the beginning of this and the last year, I did not feel at all – as one might think – superior to these thoughts, advanced; on the contrary, I regretted having gotten away from the habit of making notes. Afterwards I wanted to write something again, but I noticed that my present thinking does not move at all in [[Form]]s that can be written.\""
